high_descs: Turn left, go forward, then turn right to go toward the lamp.
Pick up the statue on the table, to the right of the lamp.
Turn and go to the lamp to your left.
Turn off the light of the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Look at a statue by the lamp.

high_descs: Walk to the statue on the small stand to the left.
Pick up the statue from the stand.
Move slightly to the left to the front of the floor lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a statue by the dim natural light of a living room.

high_descs: Go to the left and face the small table with the statue to the left of the couch.
Pick the statue up from the small table.
Go a bit more to stand in front of the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Turn a lamp on with a statue in hand.
